{"tid":355464,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"除左太宰治 有咩日本作家推介","createTime":"2017-08-11T10:08:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-19T09:03:47.000Z","uid":51796,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dce7effa4ee5907c6846459a5c9ffe097a26987a","tid":355464,"uid":51796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T10:08:22.000Z","msg":"「生而為人，我很抱歉」- 人間失格<br />\n<br />\n睇左佢d作品<br />\n好鐘意佢果種頹廢沉鬱既風格<br />\n對世界感到無助 軟弱既態度<br />\n表現到人性懦弱、卑微的一面<br />\n<br />\n雖然出身名門望族 係人生勝利組 <br />\n但身世亦都好迂迴曲折<br />\n又比人踢出校 又曾經4次自殺未遂 最後同愛人殉情 終年39歲 成個人生都好戲劇性 <br />\n<br />\n體驗左日本櫻花既美學 係最美麗既時候淍謝<br />\n<br />\n想問仲有冇咩日本作家係探討人性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0de5e5dd2ab927ec648e31a340250255fabe51ed","tid":355464,"uid":51796,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T10:13:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a34b813e7e501f79ea6ae7d26d79948ddf83231e","tid":355464,"uid":74728,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T10:18:34.000Z","msg":"江戶川亂步"},{"pid":"4c22acb3dceefa81d16eebb3639a2152f017b293","tid":355464,"uid":90863,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T10:21:19.000Z","msg":"芥川龍之介"},{"pid":"99cf82bd985307ad60b5cb32532d17649f85af83","tid":355464,"uid":86828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T10:24:58.000Z","msg":"村上春樹"},{"pid":"a1ba350d15b54711d2ab221871dac1f0e5cf48ef","tid":355464,"uid":134215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T10:26:02.000Z","msg":"川端康成"},{"pid":"3b5e1cc5a5c25ca39ae6eac042ef761db55629bc","tid":355464,"uid":124991,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T10:39:21.000Z","msg":"三島由紀夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd77de74ef944d35ba9e469dca66e8b36a0472f5","tid":355464,"uid":7206,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T10:4